quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Dͻnhwere no abεn, na bosome no mu apae."
  54,2,"Na sε wͻhunu nsεnkyerεnee bi a wͻtwe wͻn ho (fri ho), na wͻka sε: ”Woi yε nkonyaa anaa naadaasεm a εbɛtwa mu“."
  54,3,"Wͻfa no atorɔsɛm, na wͻdi wͻn apεdeε hunu akyi. Na asεm biara wͻ ne berε."
  54,4,"Ampa sε (Qur’aan) de amanebͻ a afutuo ne adesua (ahodoͻ pii) wͻ mu abrε wͻn, -"
  54,5,"Adwen ne nimdeε a εkͻ aso mu (wͻ mu), nanso afutuo no ho amma wͻn mfasoͻ."
  54,6,"Enti twe wo ho fri wͻn ho. Ɛda a Ɔfrεfoͻ (Israafiil) bεfrε (wͻn) akͻ asεm kεseε mu no,"
  54,7,"(Aniwuo bεma) wabrε wͻn ani ase; wͻbɛpue afiri adakamena no mu tesε mmεbε a wͻabͻ asanteε,"
  54,8,"Wͻde mmirika tεntε na εbεkͻ Ɔfrεfoͻ no hͻ. (Saa Da no) boniayεfoͻ no bεka sε: ”Saa Da yi yε Ɛda a emu yε den! “"
  54,9,"Noa nkorͻfoͻ dii wͻn anim kan buu Y’akoa no ᴐtorofo. Wͻkaa sε: “Bͻdamfoͻ.“ Wͻkasa tiaa no, hunahunaa no, poo no."
  54,10,"Enti osu frεε ne Wura Nyankopͻn sε: (Awurade) “Wͻabu afa me so, enti boa (me)“."
  54,11,"Enti Yɛbuee ͻsoro apono maa nsuo hwie guu pii,"
  54,12,"Yεmaa nsuwa-nsuwa nso puee wͻ asaase no so, na (ͻsoro ne asaase so) nsuo no hyia bͻͻ mu sεdeε yɛahyehyε ato hͻ no."
  54,13,"Enti Yεsoaa no wͻ (nsuom hyεn a) yεde nnua ne nnadewa na ayε so."
  54,14,"Na (nsuom hyεn no) nam (nsuo no so) a Y’ani hwε. (Saa nsuyire yi yε) akatua ma obia wannye annie."
  54,15,"Ampa sε, Yɛagya de ayε nsεnkyerεnee. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde bɛtu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,16,"Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε."
  54,17,"Ampa sε Yɛama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde betu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,18,"Aad (Nkorͻfoͻ no) faa no atorᴐsԑm. Na sεdeε M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε?"
  54,19,"Nokorε sε, Yεsomaa mframa denden bi a εbͻ toatoaso baa wͻn so wͻ da bͻne bi mu."
  54,20,"Ɛtetee nnipa maa wͻyεε sε akyiresua dua bi a yɛatu aseε da hͻ."
  54,21,"Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε."
  54,22,"Ampa sε Yɛama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde bɛtu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,23,"Samuudfoͻ no faa kͻkͻbͻ no atorᴐsԑm."
  54,24,"Deε wͻkaeε ne sε: “Onipa baako pε a ͻwͻ yεn mu na yɛnni n’akyi? Nokorε sε, εneε na yεwͻ ͻyera ne abͻdamsεm paa mu."
  54,25,"Enti yεn (dodoͻ yi) mu no, ͻno nko ara na εsεsε yεde Afutusεm no ma no? Daabi, ͻyε nkontomponi, asoͻden (nipa)”."
  54,26,"Ɔkyena wͻbɛhunu nea ͻyε nkontomponi, asoͻden (nipa) no."
  54,27,"Nokorε sε Yεresoma yoma bedeε de ayε wͻn nsͻhwε. Enti wodeε hwε wͻn na si aboterε."
  54,28,"Na ka kyerε wͻn sε, yɛakyε nsuo no mu ama (wͻn ne yoma no), obiara bεkͻ nsuo no mu wͻ ne berε (a yɛahyε ama no) mu."
  54,29,"Nanso wͻfrεε wͻn yͻnko no na ͻfaa (sekan) de wͻͻ (yoma) no kum no."
  54,30,"Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε."
  54,31,"Nokorε sε, Yεsomaa nteamu baako pε na εbaa wͻn soͻ, na wͻbεyεε gͻsͻͻ tesε mmabaa a awoͻ na abubu asin-asin a εwͻ mmoa adidieε."
  54,32,"Ampa sε Yɛama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde bɛtu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,33,"Lut nkorͻfoͻ no anye kͻkͻbͻ no anni."
  54,34,"Nokorε sε Yεsomaa aboͻ nsuo tͻ guu wͻn so, gyesε Lut abusuafoͻ nko ara (na asotwee no bi anka wͻn), Yεgyee wͻn wͻ anadwo a etwa toᴐ no mu."
  54,35,"(Ɛyε) adom a ɛfiri Yεn hͻ. Saa ara na Yɛtua wͻn a wͻyi (Nyankopͻn) ayε no ka."
  54,36,"Ampa sε (Lut) bͻͻ wͻn kͻkͻ wͻ Y’asotwee no ho, nanso wͻn adwen ansi wͻn pi wͻ kͻkͻ bͻ no ho."
  54,37,"Ampa sε wͻpεε sε wͻhwim n’ahͻhoͻ firi ne nsam. Na Yɛfiraa wͻn ani (kaa sε): “Ɛneε monka M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ no nhwε “."
  54,38,"Ampa sε, daa asotwee no sͻͻ wͻn mu ahomakye paa."
  54,39,"Enti monka M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ no nhwε."
  54,40,"Ampa sε Yɛayε Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no mmrε. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde bɛtu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,41,"Ampa sε kͻkͻbͻ no baa Farao nkorͻfoͻ no hͻ."
  54,42,"Wͻfaa Yε nsεnkyerεnee no nyinaa atorᴐsԑm. Enti Yεde Otumfoͻ a Ɔtumi ade nyinaa yε no Tumi no pari sͻͻ wͻn mu dendeenden."
  54,43,"Enti mo (mu) boniayεfoͻ no kyεn woi nom (a yɛaseε wͻn no)? Anaasε modeε moanya (bͻhyε) wͻ Twerεsεm no mu sε yɛayi mu afiri (asotwee no) mu?"
  54,44,"Anaasε deε wͻka ne sε: ”Yεdeε yεyε dͻm (kεseε) enti yεbɛdi nkonim?"
  54,45,"Yεbεka wͻn dͻm no agu ama wͻadane wͻn akyi adwane."
  54,46,"Aane, Dͻnhwere no ne εberε a yεde ahyε wͻn bͻ; na Dͻnhwere no ano yε den na (εyε berε nso) a emu (nsɛm) yε nyono."
  54,47,"Nokorε sε, abͻneεfoͻ no wͻ ͻyera ne abͻdamsεm paa mu."
  54,48,"Ɛda a yεbεtwe wͻn ase wͻ fͻm wͻ wͻn anim so akͻ egya no mu no, (yεbεka akyerε wͻn sε): ”Monka Ogya no atenka no nhwε “."
  54,49,"Nokorε sε Yεde nhyehyεeε na abͻ biribiara."
  54,50,"Na Y’ahyεdeε no deε εyε baako pε, εtesε wabͻ w’ani prε."
  54,51,"Ampa sε Yɛasεe (amanfoͻ bi) a na wͻte sε mo. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde bɛtu ne ho foͻ?"
  54,52,"Dwuma a wͻdie biara no nso yɛatwerε no wͻ Nwoma no mu."
  54,53,"Biribiara, ketewa ne kεseε nyinaa yɛatwerε."
  54,54,"Nokorε sε, Nyamesurofoͻ no wͻ Aheman mu ne nsubͻnten ho,"
  54,55,"Wͻ Nokorε Ahennwa no ho wͻ Ɔhene Tumfoͻ no a, Ɔtumi adeε nyinaa yε no hͻ."
